metadata.abstract: The document titled 'Militärische Verfahren' is currently a work in progress. It is intended to provide detailed information on military procedures relevant to aviation. This document is likely to cover various aspects of military operations, coordination, and communication protocols that pilots and controllers need to be aware of. The content will be essential for understanding the specific requirements and regulations that govern military flights and interactions with civilian air traffic. As it is still under development, further details and comprehensive guidelines will be added to ensure thorough coverage of the subject matter.
